# --- Local dev ---
# Leave both unset — `npm run dev` proxies /api → http://localhost:5000 (vite.config.js).

# --- Production on Vercel ---
# Set your Railway API host or full URL, no trailing slash (https:// added if you omit it):
#   VITE_API_URL=your-app.up.railway.app
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-app.up.railway.app
# Vercel injects this at build time for the browser; the serverless /api/contact proxy also
# reads VITE_API_URL at runtime, so one variable is enough after you redeploy.
#
# Optional: BACKEND_URL=... — proxy-only, if you want a different URL than VITE_API_URL (rare).
#
# VITE_API_URL=
# BACKEND_URL=
